object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
	SELECT MAX(batch_id) as batch_id
    FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
    WHERE source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
    and target_schema_name = '$$refined_schema'
    AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
)
select
distinct '$$sourcesystemcode' as contact_source_system,
'Agency' as contact_domain,
'Email' as contact_type,
case when age.email_type = 'T' then 'Reporting' ELSE null end as contact_sub_type,
'Agency Reporting Email Address' as contact_description,
ISNULL(age.originating_source_name,'NULL') as originating_source_name,
ISNULL(age.originating_load_type,'NULL') as originating_load_type,
age.adm_agency_email_row_status as contact_row_status,
'Loaded' as contact_row_load_state,
ISNULL(age.id,NULL) as contact_row_source_system_key,
'NULL' as contact_name_type,
'NULL' as contact_first_name_or_entity_name,
'NULL' as contact_middle_name_or_entity_second_name,
'NULL' as contact_last_name_or_entity_third_name,
'NULL' as contact_suffix,
'NULL' as contact_prefix_or_title,
REPLACE(REPLACE((contact_first_name_or_entity_name || ' ' || contact_middle_name_or_entity_second_name || ' ' || contact_last_name_or_entity_third_name || ', ' || contact_suffix),'NULL ',''),'NULL','') as contact_full_name,
ISNULL(age.email_address,'NULL') as contact_value,
'NULL' as address_id,
'NULL' as contact_rank,
ISNULL(age.create_date,'1900-01-01 00:00:00') as contact_source_system_created_datetime,
ISNULL(age.modified_date,'1900-01-01 00:00:00') as contact_source_system_modified_datetime,
cb.batch_id as batch_id,
tgt.contact_id as tgt_contact_id,
tgt.contact_row_source_system_key as tgt_contact_row_source_system_key,
tgt.contact_row_md5checksum as tgt_contact_row_md5checksum
FROM $$staging_schema.adm_agency_email age
left join 
(select 
	contact_id,
	contact_row_source_system_key,
	contact_row_md5checksum
from $$refined_schema.contacts
where contact_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00') tgt 
on tgt.contact_row_source_system_key = age.id 
cross join current_batch cb
WHERE adm_agency_email_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000000'

fields.expression:
MD5(
'contact_name_type' || contact_name_type ||
'contact_first_name_or_entity_name' || contact_first_name_or_entity_name ||
'contact_middle_name_or_entity_second_name' || contact_middle_name_or_entity_second_name ||
'contact_last_name_or_entity_third_name' || contact_last_name_or_entity_third_name ||
'contact_suffix' || contact_suffix ||
'contact_prefix_or_title' || contact_prefix_or_title ||
'contact_full_name' || contact_full_name ||
'contact_value' || contact_value ||
'address_id' || address_id ||
'contact_rank' || contact_rank
)
